BLDROW50 MVI   OVERSZ,0                                                         
         BAS   RE,ADDREPL                                                       
*&&US                                                                           
         TM    KYWIND6,KYWADA            Average days allowed?                  
         BZ    *+16                      . NO                                   
         TM    CFKIND,CFKDDBAL+CFKDBBAL  Average days wanted?                   
         BZ    *+8                       . NO                                   
         BRAS  RE,CFADRCC                CASHFLOW ADAYS ROW/COL CHECK           
*&&                                                                             
