         MVC   CT5KALPH,SECALPHA   AGENCY ALPHA                                 
         L     R1,=AL4(IOREAD+IOCNTRL+IOAREA2)                                  
         GOTO1 AIO                                                              
         BNE   FMTINI40                                                         
