         SR    R1,R1                                                            
         L     R2,AIO2                                                          
         LA    R2,CT5DATA                                                       
*                                                                               
         USING CTSEAD,R2                                                        
FMTINI30 CLI   0(R2),0                                                          
         BE    FMTINI40                                                         
         CLI   CTSEAEL,CTSEAELQ    X'B8' SECURITY ALPHA                         
         BNE   *+10                                                             
         MVC   SECALPHA,CTSEAAID   SAVE OFF SECECT'S ALPHA AGENCY               
