         USING NMEKEYD,R3                                                       
FMTINI40 L     R3,=A(NMEKEYS)                                                   
FMTINI41 CLI   0(R3),EOT                                                        
         JE    FMTINI44                                                         
         SR    R2,R2                                                            
         ICM   R2,3,NMETAB                                                      
         AR    R2,RA                                                            
         NI    0(R2),TURNOFF-X'80' Turn off built bit                           
         L     RE,0(,R2)           A(Table)                                     
         SHI   RE,2                                                             
         XC    0(2,RE),0(RE)       Clear number of entries                      
         AHI   R3,NMEKEYQ                                                       
         J     FMTINI41                                                         
*                                                                               
FMTINI44 L     R3,=A(NMEKEY2)                                                   
FMTINI45 CLI   0(R3),EOT                                                        
         JE    FMTINI90                                                         
         SR    R2,R2                                                            
         ICM   R2,3,NMETAB                                                      
         AR    R2,RA                                                            
         NI    0(R2),TURNOFF-X'80' Turn off built bit                           
         L     RE,0(,R2)           A(Table)                                     
         SHI   RE,2                                                             
         XC    0(2,RE),0(RE)       Clear number of entries                      
         AHI   R3,NMEKEYQ                                                       
         J     FMTINI45                                                         
*                                                                               
FMTINI90 XIT1                                                                   
                                                                                
         LTORG                                                                  
         DROP  R2,R3,R7                                                         
         EJECT ,                                                                
