         LA    R0,2                ONLY DO TWICE, DATE1 THEN DATE2              
*                                                                               
DTECAL08 L     RE,POINTER                                                       
         XC    RRWEL(RRWLNQ+7),RRWEL                                            
         MVI   RRWEL,RRWELQ        ROW ELEMENT CODE, X'C2'                      
         MVI   RRWLN,RRWNLNQ+6     ROW ELEMENT LENGTH                           
