         BE    DTECAL20                                                         
         CLI   0(R4),C'-'          MINUS SIGN                                   
         BE    DTECAL20                                                         
         LA    R4,1(,R4)                                                        
         B     DTECAL10                                                         
*                                                                               
DTECAL20 LR    R1,R4               SAVE LOCATION AT SO FAR                      
         L     RE,POINTER                                                       
