         MVC   HIGHSEQ,RRWSEQ      SAVE GREATER NUMBER                          
         MVC   RRWNDATA(6),SPACES  FORCE DATA TO BE LENGTH 6                    
         SR    R1,R0               FIGURE OUT LENGTH SCANED                     
         MVI   RRWDATLN,6          FORCE LENGTH TO 6                            
*        STC   R1,RRWDATLN         SAVE OFF LENGTH OF DATA                      
