DMPTAB34 MVC   WORK,SPACES                                                      
         MVC   WORK(10),=C' Keyword ='                                          
         LA    R7,WORK+11                                                       
         LA    R3,COLLNQ(,R3)                                                   
         BCT   R0,DMPTAB20                                                      
         DROP  R3,R6                                                            
