         USING TMPELD,R3                                                        
         AH    R3,DATADISP                                                      
         SR    RF,RF                                                            
         XC    COSTSMOA,COSTSMOA                                                
         XC    COSTEMOA,COSTEMOA                                                
SETCT51A CLI   0(R3),0             END OF RECORD                                
