         ZAP   RATEBEN$,PKZERO                                                  
         ZAP   RATEPEN,PKZERO                                                   
         ZAP   RATEPEN$,PKZERO                                                  
         ZAP   RATETOT,PKZERO                                                   
         ZAP   RATETOT$,PKZERO                                                  
         LA    R6,RATEBUKQ(,R6)    BUMP UP BUCKETS ONLY                         
         LA    R4,MTHDLNQ(,R4)                                                  
         BCT   R0,SETCST54                                                      
