SETCST68 SR    R1,R1                                                            
         IC    R1,1(,R3)                                                        
         AR    R3,R1                                                            
         B     SETCST64                                                         
*                                                                               
SETCST75 OC    MTHDTOT,MTHDSAL     SET ALL CODES THAT APPLY                     
         OC    MTHDTOT,MTHDBEN                                                  
         OC    MTHDTOT,MTHDPEN                                                  
         OC    MTHDTOT,MTHDIDR                                                  
         LA    R4,MTHDLNQ(,R4)                                                  
         BCT   R0,SETCST62                                                      
