SETCOSTX XMOD1 1                                                                
         DROP  R2,R3,R4,R5,R6,R7                                                
         SPACE 3                                                                
         LTORG                                                                  
         TITLE 'SET ACMCAM FOR MULTIPLE METHODS'                                
