         BNE   *+6                                                              
         DC    H'00'                                                            
         CLI   0(R3),NAMELQ        X'20' NAME                                   
         BE    GET1N25                                                          
         CLI   0(R3),RSTELQ        X'30' RECORD STATUS                          
         BE    GET1N30                                                          
