         USING NAMELD,R3                                                        
         SR    R1,R1                                                            
         IC    R1,NAMLN                                                         
         SHI   R1,NAMLN1Q                                                       
         STC   R1,NAMLEN           SAVE LENGTH OF ENTRY                         
         BCTR  R1,0                1 LESS FOR EXMVC                             
         SAM31                                                                  
         L     RE,APOOLPTR              A(NAME POOL)                            
         STCM  RE,15,NAMADR        SAVE A(NON-CLIENT NAME)                      
