         LA    RE,1(R1,RE)         NEXT AVAILABLE AREA IN NAME POOL             
         ST    RE,APOOLPTR         NEW  A(NAME POOL)                            
         C     RE,APOOLEOT         PAST END ?                                   
         SAM24                                                                  
         BNH   GET1N22             LOOP TO NEXT ELEMENT                         
         DC    H'00'               POOL FULL                                    
         DROP  R6                                                               
