         L     R5,AIO3                                                          
         MVC   ACTKACT,ACTKACT-ACTRECD(R5)                                      
         MVI   ACTKACT+L'ACTKACT,X'FF'                                          
         LA    R4,NONCLNQ(,R4)                                                  
