LSTMBLSR EQU   X'04'               .  Billing source                            
LSTMSCAN EQU   X'02'               .  Data in Scan block                        
LSTMDLNK EQU   X'01'               .  DDLink data  block                        
SCANWORK DS    CL42                                                             
         DROP  R2,R4                                                            
         SPACE 2                                                                
         LTORG                                                                  
         EJECT                                                                  
